OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774210270
OL,3,COne of the last remaining D-Day
OL,4,Cveterans has died aged 101
OL,6,FOne of the North West's last remaining
OL,7,FD-Day veterans has died aged 101.
OL,9,FJohn Dennett, from Wirral, served as a
OL,10,Fgunner on a tank landing craft which
OL,11,Flanded on Sword Beach in June 1944.
OL,13,FHe died peacefully surrounded by
OL,14,Ffamily and friends.
OL,16,FHe joined the Royal Navy at the age of
OL,17,F17 in March 1942.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
