OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774210270
OL,3,COne of the last remaining D-Day
OL,4,Cveterans has died aged 101
OL,6,FHe was an anti-aircraft gunner on one
OL,7,Fof the 7,000 ships which took soldiers
OL,8,Fto the beaches in Normandy on 6 June
OL,9,F1944, to make sure they did not get
OL,10,Fshot from overhead.
OL,12,FThe D-Day landings saw 156,000 Allied
OL,13,Ftroops arrive for a combined naval,
OL,14,Fair and land assault on Nazi-occupied
OL,15,FFrance.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774210270
OL,3,COne of the last remaining D-Day
OL,4,Cveterans has died aged 101
OL,6,FAt least 4,414 troops were killed and
OL,7,Fanother 5,900 were listed as missing
OL,8,For wounded during the operation, which
OL,9,Fwas the largest amphibious invasion in
OL,10,Fmilitary history, and marked the start
OL,11,Fof the long campaign to liberate North-
OL,12,FWest Europe from Nazi occupation.
OL,14,FJohn was one of at least 30 D-Day
OL,15,Fveterans who travelled on a ferry back
OL,16,Fto those beaches in France for special
OL,17,Fcommemorations to mark the 80th
OL,18,Fanniversary in June 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774210270
OL,3,COne of the last remaining D-Day
OL,4,Cveterans has died aged 101
OL,6,FHe told Granada Reports at the time:
OL,7,F"To me, this is a time of remembrance
OL,8,Ffor what happened all those years ago,
OL,9,F80 years is a long time.
OL,11,F"We lost thousands, a lot of mothers
OL,12,Fnever saw their sons again".
OL,14,FJust before his 100th birthday in July
OL,15,F2024, he told ITV News he lives life
OL,16,Fto the full and never takes anything
OL,17,Ffor granted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774210270
OL,3,COne of the last remaining D-Day
OL,4,Cveterans has died aged 101
OL,6,F"Live every minute because life is
OL,7,Fprecious, and so is freedom, and we
OL,8,Fgot freedom so enjoy it while you can,
OL,9,Fand treasure it," he said.
OL,11,FJohn was awarded an MBE in the 2023
OL,12,FNew Years' Honours list, the first
OL,13,Funder King Charles, not just for what
OL,14,Fhe's done for his country, but also
OL,15,Ffor what he's done for his community.
OL,17,FAfter the end of the second World War,
OL,18,Fin 1949, John and his wife Joyce,
OL,19,Fstarted a junior football team in
OL,20,FWallasey, Ashville FC, named after the
OL,21,Froad they lived on.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774210270
OL,3,COne of the last remaining D-Day
OL,4,Cveterans has died aged 101
OL,6,FOver 75 years later, the club is still
OL,7,Fvery much ongoing.
OL,9,FIn July 2023, to mark his 99th
OL,10,Fbirthday, the renowned Merseyside
OL,11,Fstreet artist Paul Curtis painted a
OL,12,Fmural of John on the wall of Ashville
OL,13,FFC's clubhouse.
OL,15,FPaul said: "This project was a real
OL,16,Fprivilege for me.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774210270
OL,3,COne of the last remaining D-Day
OL,4,Cveterans has died aged 101
OL,6,F"I have painted murals for
OL,7,Ffootballers, actors, musicians -
OL,8,Fpeople we quickly idolise as heroes,
OL,9,Fbut we often forget the true heroes
OL,10,Fthat don't have that fame or glamour,
OL,11,Fbut did more for us than we can
OL,12,Fimagine."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
